name: 'Will and Dot's Terrific Tree House' book
description:
A limited edition hardback copy of Will and Dot's first adventure picturebook.

SIZE - B5 (250 x 176 mm = 9.8" x 6.9")
Printed on recycled, FSC certified paper.

Post and packing is £2 for a single item and an additional £1.50 for each extra item ordered at the same time to a single address. £6 for international orders plus £2 for each additional item.

Estimated delivery time is 5 days.  

DISCOUNTS AVAILABLE FOR
- Original Kickstarter Backers
- Bulk and repeat orders
- Those able to collect their book in person (at sellers discretion)
Email info@willanddot.com to request codes if applicable.

name: 'The Perfect Tree' Limited Edition Print 1
description:
Signed and numbered print of one of the many illustrations within the picture book. Only a maximum of 100 signed copies will be released.
Size information:
Paper size A3 (279 x 420 mm), printed area sits within a 4cm (approx) white margin.

Post and packing is £3.50 for up to 5 prints ordered at the same time to a single address. £7 for international orders of the same quantity.
